g in poverty or being sick \u2013 all the things you have to deal with must seem insurmountable. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So here\u2019s the good news: we are giving our music to charities so they can play them at live events \u2013 where people can come out, listen to great music and be part of something bigger.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We believe that music has an incredible power to heal and bring life back into focus, especially when surrounded by people who care about you. <\/p>\n<a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/2022\/02\/18\/help-people-in-need\/\">Read More<\/a>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":140,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-137","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-uncategorized"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/137","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=137"}],"version-history":[{"count":15,"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/137\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":200,"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/137\/revisions\/200"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/140"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.vivathemes.com\/bass\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=137"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https